Package: tgpipe
Architecture: all
Depends: bash, curl, ${misc:Depends}
Description: Pipe anything into Telegram
 tgpipe is a tiny CLI tool that sends text, logs, files and other data
 to Telegram using the Bot API. Designed for DevOps, monitoring,
 cron jobs, systemd timers and home automation.
